    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Take to your local river with the ASR Outdoor 5pc Beginner&#039;s Gold Panning Kit! This set comes with everything you&#039;ll need to pan for gold, examine and store gold flakes, gold flour or small gold nuggets, or other gems, fossils or precious metals found when gold panning.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 5pc Gold Pan Gold Prospecting Tools Beginners Kit (Many Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Take to your local river with the ASR Outdoor 5pc Beginner&#039;s Gold Panning Kit! This set comes with everything you&#039;ll need to pan for gold, examine and store gold flakes, gold flour or small gold nuggets, or other gems, fossils or precious metals found when gold panning.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>SIZE OF GOLD PAN - 12&quot; or 14&quot; Diameter | Dual Riffle for Sifting Pay Dirt for Gold Nuggets</li>\n    <li>LARGE COLLECTION TOOL - for Storing Findings; 2 Dram Capacity</li>\n    <li>MAGNIFYING LOUPE - Magnification Loupe for Checking the Quality of Recovered Gold and Precious Gems</li>\n    <li>SIZE OF TWEEZERS - 5.5&quot; L</li>\n    <li>SIZE OF PLASTIC RECOVERY TOOL - 3oz Capacity</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/sports_outdoors/gold_panning/pans/5pc_beginner_kit_parent.jpg\" alt=\"Take to your local river with the ASR Outdoor 5pc Beginner&#039;s Gold Panning Kit\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 5PCBEGGPPARENT</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>In the beginner gold panning kit, we&#039;ve included one of our most popular gold pan sizes: the gold pan features dual riffles (coarse and fine) that will assist you in separating gold from other unwanted materials like gravels, sands and rocks. The dual riffle gold pan is molded from one piece of high impact, ABS plastic; the gold pan is very lightweight, rust resistant, UV resistant, waterproof and it floats! This pan is unseasoned so be sure to clean off before use for best results.</p>\n  <p>As for gold prospecting equipment accessories, this kit comes with a magnifying loupe that you&#039;ll be able to use to evaluate the quality of any found objects that may be of value. A few of the other items included are fine gold recovery tools for collecting, cleaning and storing your findings. This is a great kit for beginner gold prospectors who are looking to experiment and get their hands dirty with this fun and challenging outdoor sport or hobby.</p>\n  <p>PLEASE NOTE: Gold pan colors come assorted in high contrast colors of blue, deep green and black.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
